---
import { TRANSLATIONS } from '../consts';

const t = TRANSLATIONS.zh;
---

<section class="bejamas-section bejamas-base">
  <div class="bejamas-container">
    <div class="bejamas-section-header bejamas-text-center">
      <h2 class="bejamas-title-2xl bejamas-heading">{t.customerReviewsTitle}</h2>
      <p class="bejamas-subtitle bejamas-mt-2">听听我们的客户怎么说</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bejamas-reviews-grid">
      <div class="bejamas-review-card">
        <div class="bejamas-review-header">
          <div class="bejamas-review-avatar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="张伟" />
          </div>
          <div class="bejamas-review-info">
            <h4 class="bejamas-review-name">张伟</h4>
            <p class="bejamas-review-company">中亚重工集团</p>
            <div class="bejamas-review-rating">
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-content">
          <p>"HPF.kz为我们的大型设备运输提供了专业服务。从中国到哈萨克斯坦的全程跟踪非常透明，让我们能够实时了解货物状态。"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-tags">
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">超尺物流</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">项目物流</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">专业服务</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bejamas-review-card">
        <div class="bejamas-review-header">
          <div class="bejamas-review-avatar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="李明" />
          </div>
          <div class="bejamas-review-info">
            <h4 class="bejamas-review-name">李明</h4>
            <p class="bejamas-review-company">新疆矿业公司</p>
            <div class="bejamas-review-rating">
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-content">
          <p>"危特品运输一直是我们最担心的问题。HPF.kz的专业团队确保了所有合规要求，运输过程安全可靠，让我们非常放心。"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-tags">
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">危特品合规</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">安全运输</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">专业团队</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bejamas-review-card">
        <div class="bejamas-review-header">
          <div class="bejamas-review-avatar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="王芳" />
          </div>
          <div class="bejamas-review-info">
            <h4 class="bejamas-review-name">王芳</h4>
            <p class="bejamas-review-company">中亚电商平台</p>
            <div class="bejamas-review-rating">
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-content">
          <p>"作为跨境电商，时效性对我们至关重要。HPF.kz提供了完美的时效成本平衡方案，让我们的客户体验大幅提升。"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-tags">
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">跨境电商</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">时效性</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">成本优化</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bejamas-review-card">
        <div class="bejamas-review-header">
          <div class="bejamas-review-avatar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="陈强" />
          </div>
          <div class="bejamas-review-info">
            <h4 class="bejamas-review-name">陈强</h4>
            <p class="bejamas-review-company">汽车零部件制造商</p>
            <div class="bejamas-review-rating">
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-content">
          <p>"CKD/SKD零部件的运输要求非常高。HPF.kz的专业包装和运输方案确保了零部件的完好无损，大大降低了我们的损失率。"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-tags">
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">CKD/SKD</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">专业包装</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">零部件运输</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bejamas-review-card">
        <div class="bejamas-review-header">
          <div class="bejamas-review-avatar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="刘洋" />
          </div>
          <div class="bejamas-review-info">
            <h4 class="bejamas-review-name">刘洋</h4>
            <p class="bejamas-review-company">零售连锁企业</p>
            <div class="bejamas-review-rating">
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-content">
          <p>"高频补货需求对物流时效要求极高。HPF.kz的温控协同运输确保了生鲜产品的质量，让我们的库存管理更加健康。"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-tags">
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">高频补货</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">温控运输</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">库存管理</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bejamas-review-card">
        <div class="bejamas-review-header">
          <div class="bejamas-review-avatar">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="赵敏" />
          </div>
          <div class="bejamas-review-info">
            <h4 class="bejamas-review-name">赵敏</h4>
            <p class="bejamas-review-company">定制解决方案客户</p>
            <div class="bejamas-review-rating">
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
              <span class="bejamas-star bejamas-star-filled">★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-content">
          <p>"我们的业务需求非常特殊，HPF.kz为我们提供了完全定制化的解决方案。从咨询到实施，全程专业高效，超出了我们的预期。"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bejamas-review-tags">
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">定制方案</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">专业高效</span>
          <span class="bejamas-review-tag">超出预期</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bejamas-reviews-stats">
      <div class="bejamas-stat-item">
        <h3 class="bejamas-stat-number">500+</h3>
        <p class="bejamas-stat-label">满意客户</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bejamas-stat-item">
        <h3 class="bejamas-stat-number">98%</h3>
        <p class="bejamas-stat-label">客户满意度</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bejamas-stat-item">
        <h3 class="bejamas-stat-number">1000+</h3>
        <p class="bejamas-stat-label">成功项目</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bejamas-stat-item">
        <h3 class="bejamas-stat-number">5年</h3>
        <p class="bejamas-stat-label">行业经验</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bejamas-reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--bejamas-space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-12);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .bejamas-reviews-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .bejamas-reviews-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-card {
    background-color: var(--bejamas-color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--bejamas-color-border);
    border-radius: var(--bejamas-radius-xl);
    padding: var(--bejamas-space-6);
    transition: all var(--bejamas-transition-base);
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--bejamas-shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--bejamas-space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-4);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--bejamas-color-bg-muted);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-info {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-name {
    font-size: var(--bejamas-text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bejamas-color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-1);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-company {
    color: var(--bejamas-color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--bejamas-text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-2);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-rating {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--bejamas-space-1);
  }
  
  .bejamas-star {
    color: var(--bejamas-color-border);
    font-size: var(--bejamas-text-lg);
  }
  
  .bejamas-star-filled {
    color: var(--bejamas-color-yellow-500);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-content {
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-4);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-content p {
    color: var(--bejamas-color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--bejamas-space-2);
  }
  
  .bejamas-review-tag {
    background-color: var(--bejamas-color-bg-muted);
    color: var(--bejamas-color-text-muted);
    padding: var(--bejamas-space-1) var(--bejamas-space-3);
    border-radius: var(--bejamas-radius-full);
    font-size: var(--bejamas-text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .bejamas-reviews-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--bejamas-space-8);
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .bejamas-reviews-stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      max-width: none;
    }
  }
  
  .bejamas-stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .bejamas-stat-number {
    font-size: var(--bejamas-text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bejamas-color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-1);
  }
  
  .bejamas-stat-label {
    color: var(--bejamas-color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--bejamas-text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  /* Spacing utilities */
  .bejamas-mt-2 { margin-top: var(--bejamas-space-2); }
  .bejamas-mb-4 { margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-4); }
  .bejamas-mb-12 { margin-bottom: var(--bejamas-space-12); }
  
  .bejamas-text-center { text-align: center; }
</style>